How to build a notification. 

1) Create a Notification channel.
2) Create a NotificationUtil class in a Util package.
3) In the NotificationUtil class create build the notification
4) Show the notification in the status bar. 



1) Create a Notification channel
A notification channel repesents a number settings that apply to a collection of similarly themed notifications. Starting in API 26+ all notifictions must be assigned to a channel. 
After you create a notification channel, you cannot change the notification behaviors, the user has complete control of the behaviors at this point. 

